data.text:
Michael P. Downey is a legal ethics lawyer and founder of Downey Law Group LLC, A St. Louis law firm devoted to legal ethics, lawyer discipline defense and the law of lawyering. Michael regularly advised lawyers at law firms and legal departments regarding legal ethics and risk management issues. Michael also assists lawyers responding to disciplinary complaints and has defended lawyers in civil litigation and disciplinary cases in both Missouri and Illinois.

Learn more about Michael and his practice at DowneyLawGroup.com.
